Welcome to pairsdblib.

pairsdblib is free software. Please see the file COPYING for details.
For documentation, please see the files in the doc subdirectory.
For building and installation instructions please see the INSTALL file.

Specific installation instructions:

To install on gaia, run the following sequence of commands:

tar -xvzf pairsdblib-x.x.x.tar.gz
cd pairsdblib-x.x.x.tar.gz
./configure --prefix=/afs/bi/bioinfo/group --with-boost=/afs/bi/bioinfo/group --with-alignlib-dir=/afs/bi/bioinfo/group
make
make install

